name: YOU ARE MORE THAN YOUR DAY JOB
description: This one is for everybody out there working day jobs (or whatever your hustle) is in order to pursue your dreams. I created "YOU ARE MORE THAN YOUR DAY JOB" as a reminder that you are doing this for a reason and you know what you're working for. This piece is originally hand-drawn and later digitally colored in Procreate. This is a TOMORROWMAN original artwork. Stay on your grind and keep on dreaming!
